{
  "stem": "3097.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent me to Korea instead to Europe, you see, where I could do much more better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They send me over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were panic-- panicky at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few words, only.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very-- it was a very, very primitive country at that time because, you know, Japanese occupation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They really exploited the country very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now it's completely different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I-- when I passed the license, and I settled in Chicago-- Chicago, went on the south side, where my friend used to have a practice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wrote me I should go with him in general practice, but I had already 16 months of my residency, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I invested already that much time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I finished my residency, and I settled on the south side there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was about 250 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a temple, a rabbi, and so forth, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they dissipated in Scottsdale, and the community dissipated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked myself up to be a consultant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was chairman of the department for three years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- At Michael Reese?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, at the Rush Medical School, Rush [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a consultant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I'm ready to retire now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm ready to-- to-- July 1, another three weeks or, what, 20 days, three Mondays-- to finish my career as a physician.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, I have to see what happens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I taught all my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think I have to do-- I-- I have some hobbies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I write.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wrote some poetry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- maybe I will hone it a little bit better yet, you see, because I will have time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could never read anything besides medicine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
